{"tid":1438583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和你飛] 機場文宣方向！！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T20:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:22:00.000Z","uid":22607,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"29d10e9b8cc81ec28c214ce8272b942bf217f0d1","tid":1438583,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:41:34.000Z","msg":"琴日有份接機，見到現場好多文宣，全部都好靚好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係跟據我嘅觀察，<span style=\"color: red;\">會認真停落黎睇嘅好大部分人都係同路香港人，而旅客就會一邊行一邊睇。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，係輸出資訊方面，詳細多字嘅文宣好似作用未算好大。<br />\n<br />\n我琴晚現場畫左一張好簡單嘅文宣，A4 size，內容淨係寫左黑警放過期催淚彈，黑白大字報咁，再貼係自己個口罩出面同行黎行去。<br />\n<br />\n發現咁樣好似簡潔清晰啲，成功吸引到旅客嘅目光，所以想集思廣益，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊設計大字報，一張紙淨係寫一句資訊，再貼係自己到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等我拋下磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申:唔識design<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/naFsX3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnaFsX3f.jpg&h=d2f8d8df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DQAnuW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DQAnuW.jpg&h=65dcb640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcHGh3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcHGh3g.jpg&h=a964eac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujOVnuX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujOVnuX.jpg&h=2efbb044&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9826996a9de5675ecf0a03230d0461d082efe5b6","tid":1438583,"uid":119485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:42:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n香港人重點日程：<br />\n8月9-11日：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)<br />\n8月10日：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n8月10日：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n8月10日：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）<br />\n8月11日：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n8月11日：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFF4YRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFF4YRE.jpg&h=539785ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9Lc7Li.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9Lc7Li.jpg&h=8d1626e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFLHLw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFLHLw8.jpg&h=d8fae00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaMsLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaMsLz.jpg&h=b4f4136d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1PqYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1PqYA.jpg&h=5a975883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQEdSDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQEdSDA.jpg&h=da0e19d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/276scxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F276scxO.jpg&h=78ce765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af95J0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf95J0h.jpg&h=5304a0a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f179e9fcde65e6b48b2898ccbd0f0b42f434e6f","tid":1438583,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec027b38f32c111cdd77f657f0b42f78b89c214b","tid":1438583,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:42:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc88414c7dcfc03af307d4a400bf0981dab60bc","tid":1438583,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"424d48b517fdb6d5c7445ec6cdd19eae81d61d1a","tid":1438583,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":