d6fe231dce1c3428c542a019848","tid":1438583,"uid":260903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:43:40.000Z","msg":"文宣 group 轉過嚟：<br />\n<br />\n【萬人摺機】文宣，求文字內容、illustrator 接力<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我諗到一個文宣嘅 idea，就係摺紙飛機。但我文字功力唔好，亦都唔係 Ai 能手，所以只起左個 grid。如果呢度有高手，覺得有得做，懇請接手（ai 檔 link 在下面），感謝！<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n &bull; 有 gimmick，可吸引眼球（希望有記者影），亦為博君一笑<br />\n &bull; 有動手做（hands-on）元素，大家坐得悶、嗌得攰嘅時候可以做<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n &bull; 工序上除左摺，可能需剪裁（普通影印舖印出嚟會有 margin）<br />\n &bull; 俾人屈話係攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：摺嚟唔係預大家掟，係派俾旅客<br />\n<br />\nAI 檔: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Thf3GI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Thf3GI&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9b62ff31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Thf3GI</a><br />\nPDF 檔: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33neIXQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33neIXQ&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=811c178d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33neIXQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oc2K0Cu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOc2K0Cu.jpg&h=978d5571&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BipEPvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBipEPvQ.jpg&h=5c7bac24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9747f50c7de488d7db50df9d099fa44f81462619","tid":1438583,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f65f0e8a713d77de47f1c87e88a172bf4e8819","tid":1438583,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c94208e9d7e6b75131e0448130ce92eb69b4e0","tid":1438583,"uid":293077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>話比遊客知，唔好著黑衫，唔好出街，因為隨時會比黑警拉比黑社會打同食TG</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n搞冧旅遊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d7fd95c4933ecbdccd4df82aa1ecde07f08b08","tid":1438583,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2133574b946889d4589d84ea6d037ced499dae24","tid":1438583,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:32:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>Stay Safe in Hong Kong</strong><br />\n呢句吸引咗遊客注意先<br />\n之後再講警察有幾危險"},{"pid":"50fa85a70f2f29d2795080e4f642b6d918dc412a","tid":1438583,"uid":302212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXJimof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXJimof.jpg&h=02848364&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5qkzJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5qkzJg.jpg&h=e2d96d36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e877a971771bbe8a89be14356953de78860b109","tid":1438583,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:25:00.000Z","msg":"機場文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n文宣商戰：撐「五大訴求、缺一不可」良心認證標誌店舖消費推廣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e3c484f78cb981e887be0560cbe8e9f6958a55a","tid":1438583,"uid":51064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"